-tGQWv4Q_l_UC3oc\",\"summary\":[]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_a6m51L7H6cfFYL1OfXoHiyUT|fc_0e7574659754201b016a25f871dbe88190b6c77484a1948855", "name": "write", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/org.bouncycastle/bcprov-jdk18on/1.77/src/test/java/org_bouncycastle/bcprov_jdk18on/JCEECPrivateKeyTest.java", "content": "/*\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\n *\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\n */\npackage org_bouncycastle.bcprov_jdk18on;\n\nimport org.bouncycastle.jce.ECNamedCurveTable;\nimport org.bouncycastle.jce.provider.JCEECPrivateKey;\nimport org.bouncycastle.jce.spec.ECNamedCurveParameterSpec;\nimport org.bouncycastle.jce.spec.ECNamedCurveSpec;\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\n\nimport java.io.ByteArrayInputStream;\nimport java.io.ByteArrayOutputStream;\nimport java.io.ObjectInputStream;\nimport java.io.ObjectOutputStream;\nimport java.math.BigInteger;\nimport java.security.spec.ECPrivateKeySpec;\n\nimport static org.assertj.core.api.Assertions.assertThat;\n\npublic class JCEECPrivateKeyTest {\n    private static final BigInteger PRIVATE_VALUE = new BigInteger(\n            \"1122334455667788990011223344556677889900112233445566778899001122\");\n\n    @Test\n    void serializesAndRestoresJceEcPrivateKeyParameters() throws Exception {\n        JCEECPrivateKey original = newJceEcPrivateKey();\n        original.setPointFormat(\"COMPRESSED\");\n\n        JCEECPrivateKey restored = deserialize(serialize(original));\n\n        assertThat(restored.getD()).isEqualTo(original.getD());\n        assertThat(restored.getS()).isEqualTo(original.getS());\n        assertThat(restored.getParams().getOrder()).isEqualTo(original.getParams().getOrder());\n        assertThat(restored.getParams().getGenerator()).isEqualTo(original.getParams().getGenerator());\n        assertThat(restored.getParameters().getN()).isEqualTo(original.getParameters().getN());\n        assertThat(restored.getAlgorithm()).isEqualTo(\"EC\");\n        assertThat(restored.getFormat()).isEqualTo(\"PKCS#8\");\n        assertThat(restored.getEncoded()).isNotEmpty();\n        assertThat(restored.getBagAttributeKeys().hasMoreElements()).isFalse();\n    }\n\n    private static JCEECPrivateKey newJceEcPrivateKey() {\n        ECNamedCurveParameterSpec namedCurve = ECNamedCurveTable.getParameterSpec(\"secp256r1\");\n        ECNamedCurveSpec namedCurveSpec = new ECNamedCurveSpec(\n                \"secp256r1\",\n                namedCurve.getCurve(),\n                namedCurve.getG(),\n                namedCurve.getN(),\n                namedCurve.getH(),\n                namedCurve.getSeed());\n        ECPrivateKeySpec privateKeySpec = new ECPrivateKeySpec(PRIVATE_VALUE, namedCurveSpec);\n\n        return new JCEECPrivateKey(\"EC\", privateKeySpec);\n    }\n\n    private static byte[] serialize(JCEECPrivateKey privateKey) throws Exception {\n        ByteArrayOutputStream serialized = new ByteArrayOutputStream();\n        try (ObjectOutputStream objectOutputStream = new ObjectOutputStream(serialized)) {\n            objectOutputStream.writeObject(privateKey);\n        }\n        return serialized.toByteArray();\n    }\n\n    private static JCEECPrivateKey deserialize(byte[] serialized) throws Exception {\n        try (ObjectInputStream objectInputStream = new ObjectInputStream(new ByteArrayInputStream(serialized))) {\n            return (JCEECPrivateKey)objectInputStream.readObject();\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 535, "output": 1886, "cacheRead": 19968, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 22389, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1780873304874, "responseId": "resp_0e7574659754201b016a25f8597d9081908d9a84dfedf5e389"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_a6m5